des a plausible explanation for the gamma-ray flares in the Crab\nNebula and could be at work in other astrophysical objects such as relativistic\njets in active galactic nuclei.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2011 01:18:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Jan 2012 16:46:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
