ive a sufficient and necessary\ncondition on a monad in K^ to be isomorphic to an n-ary weak wreath product.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2011 12:06:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2012 10:20:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-18"}
